V Share is a full-stack social media application built with the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js). Users can register, log in, create posts, connect with friends, and interact in a modern, responsive UI.

Features:
User registration and login with JWT authentication
Email verification and password reset
Create, edit, and delete posts
Like, comment, and interact with posts
Friend requests and user profiles
Responsive design with Tailwind CSS


Tech Stack:
Frontend: React, Redux, React Router, Tailwind CSS
Backend: Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB (Mongoose)
Email: Nodemailer, Outlook SMTP
Getting Started


Prerequisites:
Node.js and npm
MongoDB Atlas account (or local MongoDB)
Git

